What you need to know:

The members from Western and North Rift regions said his bid for the presidency is unstoppable and that he has what it takes to lead Kenya in the right direction.Mr Waliaula further called on Devolution Cabinet Secretary Eugene Wamalwa and Council of Governors chair Wycliffe Oparanya (Kakamega) to stop misleading Luhyas on the presidential candidacy and support Mr Mudavadi.